 have witnessed first hand her ability to organize people and implement processes. She's very persuasive and is able to breakdown technical Dev Ops procedures into consumable chunks to the team. One of my favorite traits about Jyothi is that she always has documentation around her objectives and processes. I've collaborated with her on many projects and have always been impressed with how much substance she brought to the table with respect to QE and DevOps procedures. She was a joy to work with and I strongly recommend her for a leadership role - <strong>VP, Customer Experience</strong></span></p>
