implements Agile and Digital transformations so the team and company can scale. Jyothi collaborates with other teams to ensure she understands the needs of all stakeholders. I look forward to the opportunity to work with Jyothi again. - <strong>CEO</strong></span></p>
</div><div id="a192209ac0310267fff0207fe1e92a44" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="item "><div id="a192209ac03109635041b29cf0f4c46b" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a192209ac02f01e6ee039027bd548640" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a192209ac0300425ddb86cc908fd4049" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a192209ac02f04efc988b61fea821210" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div><div id="a192209ac030054098445b412b4f8c9c" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom8" style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Jyothi, Thank you for all you've done to bring the AI partnership to reality - <strong>Partner</strong></span></p>
</div><div id="a192209ac03103103317cd0c8f16142b" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="item "><div id="a19222200dc000898fb6bb1c0dbf5b7b" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a19222200dc8000dcc5f5c1d84a67621" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a19222200dcf00b6ee8872668a714471" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a19222200dd500d99174b356fbfb3932" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div><div id="a19222200de20047951bd36599466450" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom8">As the Head of Sales, I was able to work closely with Jyothi. She demonstrated an exceptional ability to bridge the gap between technical innovation and strategic business growth, positioning her as a strong asset for any organization looking to enhance its sales and technology framework.  </p>

<p class="wb-stl-custom8">Jyothi’s strategic mindset and leadership have been instrumental in driving organizational success. Her ability to understand complex technical landscapes and align them with business goals has consistently resulted in tangible outcomes.<span style="font-size:16px;"> </span>The initiatives she championed—improving team velocity, enhancing SDLC frameworks, and fostering cross-team collaboration—are the exact qualities required for any organization aiming to scale while maintaining high quality and efficiency.<br>
Furthermore, Jyothi’s expertise in security compliance and data protection (securing ISO certifications) ensures that any digital transformation she leads will adhere to the highest industry standards—vital for instilling confidence in both internal teams and clients.<br>
I believe her combination of technical expertise, strategic thinking, and focus on process efficiency and growth makes her an ideal candidate to drive your organization's business and technology initiatives forward.<span style="font-size:16px;">- <strong>Sr. VP of Sales</strong></span></p>
</div><div id="a19222200ded001037800cc86b15879d" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="item "><div id="a19222285ce40043ce427092eaa0587f" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a19222285cec00170eeeb4e65c714485" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a19222285cf30082fd0b13835ea4384c" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a19222285cf900af76ce0d23436330bf" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div><div id="a19222285d06004decd3834fb8eeb394" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom8">Without a doubt, I would work with Jyothi again! She embodies all the qualities needed in a manager, and someone who is dedicated to doing it the right way, every time. Without her assistance, my job would have been much more difficult. She's a great friend, too, always looking for opportunities to get to know you and understand your needs. I'm pleased to endorse her and look forward to opportunities to work with her again in the future. (Just don't play ping pong with her, because you'll lose. ;-).<span style="font-size:16px;">- <strong>Manager</strong></span></p>
</div><div id="a19222285d1100f66160384083bc285d" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="item active"><div id="a1923bb69aea00cefa1f9c630028a379" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a1923bb69aed00b540096424a2960f93" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a1923bb69af200c8fe39f5962aa9dda5" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="a1923bb69af50062dff7908e4d820df9" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div><div id="a1923bb69afc00298bec44c32e51a2fe" class="wb_element wb_text_element" data-plugin="TextArea" style=" line-height: normal;"><p class="wb-stl-custom8" style="text-align: justify;">Jyothi has not only shone in her role she has also earned the respect of those around her and won many friends in the department. </p>

<p class="wb-stl-custom8" style="text-align: justify;"> </p>

<p class="wb-stl-custom8" style="text-align: justify;">I first realized that I had a real gem on my hands, her thoroughness in her work is unmatched. Jyothi worked on several detailed system enhancements for the Premium Billing System team, in all stages of development from requirements gathering and prototyping to testing and production rollout.</p>

<p class="wb-stl-custom8" style="text-align: justify;"> </p>

<p class="wb-stl-custom8" style="text-align: justify;">Where Jyothi really shines is that she is not just a detail-conscious "techie" but she is able to communicate ideas and issues with our clients, and then take in their responses to formulate practical solutions. She does not just "perform her job" but demonstrates a keen and inquiring mind in her work, asking key questions and following through on the most difficult of issues.  And in addition, Jyothi really cares about the people on her team, showing support and encouragement to new employees, and being always ready to lend a helping hand to her co-workers. She is truly a proactive employee, and a great asset - <strong>Senior Analyst</strong></p>
</div><div id="a1923bb69b03007bd6f14e803f4a1494" class="wb_element wb_element_picture" data-plugin="Picture" title=""><div class="wb_picture_wrap"><div class="wb-picture-wrapper" style="overflow: visible; display: flex"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="auto" viewBox="0 0 1793.982 1793.982" style="direction: ltr; color:#000000"><text x="65.501415" y="1537.02" font-size="1792" fill="currentColor" style='font-family: "FontAwesome"'></text></svg></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="wb_footer_a192209abed500d49d641bfdaca00432" class="wb_element wb-layout-element" data-plugin="LayoutElement"><div class="wb_content wb-layout-vertical"><div id="wb_footer_c" class="wb_element" data-plugin="WB_Footer" style="text-align: center; width: 100%;"><div class="wb_footer"></div><script type="text/javascript">
